# T8.3.B perf artifacts — ignored by default.
#
# The schema is locked in `harness/artifact.ts` (SCHEMA_VERSION); the
# JSON files themselves carry per-run timestamps + machine-specific
# browser builds, so committing them would just churn diffs. T8.3.C's
# aggregator reads whatever is on disk at run time; T8.3.D's report
# generator likewise produces a baseline from a local run.
#
# Keep this `.gitignore` tracked so the directory exists in fresh
# checkouts (Playwright errors out trying to mkdir into a missing
# parent on some filesystems).
*.json
*.tmp.*
.playwright-summary.json
!.gitignore
